# AgendaService

AgendaService is a simple API allowing users to manage their schedules online.

# Group User

Resource operations related to a user in the API.

A User object has the following attributes:

+ id (int)
+ username (string)
+ password (string)
+ email (string)


## User-Key [/user/getkey{?username,password}]

+ Parameters
    - username : `root` (string, required) - User Name
    - password : `pass` (string, required) - User Password

### Get User Key [GET]

get a security key for operations later.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "key":"1e3576bt"
            "permissions":["user","admin"]
        }


# Group Users

Resources related to users in the API.

## Users Collection [/users{?key}]

+ Parameters
    - key : `1e3576bt` (string, required)

### List all Users [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id":1
                "username":"VinaLx"
                "password":"vpass"
                "email":"VinaLx@mail2.sysu.edu.cn"
