### Create a New User [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "username":"TestUser"
            "password":"tpass"
            "email":"TestUser@mail2.sysu.edu.cn"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /users/4

    + Body

            {
                "id": 4
                "username":"TestUser"
                "password":"tpass"
                "email":"TestUser@mail2.sysu.edu.cn"
            }

### Delete a User [DELETE /users/{id}]

+ Parameters
    - id : `4` (int, required) - User ID

+ Response 204